{"word":"ἐπιτιμάω","slug":"ἐπιτιμάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιτιμάω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to lay a value upon</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>aestimare</el>: hence,<p/></div><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to shew honour to</i>, <el>τινά</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to raise in price</i>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to rise in price</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of judges, <i>to lay a penalty on</i> a person, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to censure</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>; also <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}